This repository documents my step-by-step progress as I learn React.js from the ground up. Instead of just focusing on the final projects, I'm sharing the entire learning process—covering concepts, code examples, mini-projects, and challenges I encounter along the way.

The goal is to build a strong foundation in React while maintaining consistency and creating a public record of my growth as a developer.

Tech Stack
React.js
JavaScript (ES6+)
HTML5
CSS3
Vite
Git & GitHub

* Why i am doing this : earning is more effective when it's consistent and documented. By maintaining this repository, I hope to:

Build discipline through daily practice
Reinforce concepts by writing code
Showcase my progress and problem-solving approach
Inspire other beginners to start their own learning journey

* Feedback & Suggestions

If you have suggestions, best practices, or ideas for improvement, feel free to open an issue or start a discussion. I'm always happy to learn from the community.